fehd.ADR_TC: 香港中環荷里活道67號地庫

result.adr_address: 67號 Hollywood Rd, Central, Hong Kong
result.name: Club 71

reviews.text: One of the most authentic bars in hk. With an artsy and very liberal Flair all over the place. Attracts like minded people for a very fair price with super nice staff! Outdoors is so much space and very chill atmosphere! This place has become an institution of Hong Kong alternative places to drink!
Very nice bar frequented by artists and art professionals, right next to a gay bar. A good crowd in Hong Kong.
Very friendly staff and reasonable prices for the area.
The fruit punch here’s so good. We ordered 12cups!!!

real chill, it's situated right beside a park with another bar so there is some kind of communal mingling going on outside if there aren't any more seats inside. if you walk further into the park and down some steps, you've got a little private place to chill.
